<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天晚上7点开始有烟花大会！<delay frames="40" />
光是想象一下烟花的声响和气味。<delay20 />
我就兴奋起来了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚有烟花大会！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从晚上7点开始燃放，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不能忘记了啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">今晚7点开始的烟花大会<delay20 />真让人期待不已啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你当然也会来观看的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起享受美好的夜晚吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">一想到烟花大会马上就要开始了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就不禁紧张起来，这可不像我啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话虽如此，我只负责观赏而已啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是来看烟花的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到马上要开始，<delay20 />我就不知怎么静不下心。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要在附近散散步呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了不漏看第1枚升空的烟花，<delay20 />
我一直向上盯着天空，肩膀都僵了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明都还没正式开始啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这次的烟花大会，<delay8 />我玩得很尽兴！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我被其他人的热情感染，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知不觉间也尽情嬉闹了一番。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />我玩得无比尽兴！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看烟花会让人心情兴奋起来。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉今晚要睡不着啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会<delay8 />让岛上的气氛变得十分热烈啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多亏如此，<delay8 />我补充了一番庆典能量。<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天也能继续努力了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最后一场烟花大会<delay20 />结束了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到这是最后一眼就很不舍，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我更加期待明年的烟花大会了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的烟花，<delay8 />每一朵都很漂亮啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样闭上眼睛，<delay8 />就能够一次又一次
回想起烟花的模样～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的烟花大会也结束了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年我还想看烟花。<delay frames="40" />
像这样，<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和你一起看！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>